pgproto (0.3.3-1PIGSTY) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Upgrade to upstream 0.3.3.
  * Switch to the new vendored protobuf source bundle shared with RPM.
  * Drop the obsolete utf8_range header patch because upstream now links the
    bundled utf8_range implementation directly.

 -- Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>  Sat, 18 Apr 2026 14:05:00 +0800

